last_episode_to_air.overview: After weeks of debating with each other about how to find their matches, the singles band together and make their riskiest effort yet at finding true love.

name: Are You The One?
overview: In the most ambitious dating experiment ever attempted, a group of gorgeous single women and guys are put through an extensive and scientific matchmaking process to find their Perfect Match.

seasons.name: Season 6
seasons.overview: Set in the stunning city of New Orleans, Season 6 is tasking a crew of love hopefuls with two things: To dig deeper than ever before to find true love and to keep from screwing it all up. Though chances are, having the Big Easy as your backdrop doesn't make either of those to-do items any, er, easier.

tagline: Where in the world is your perfect match?

episodes.name: You Can't Handle the Truth
episodes.overview: 20 singles are all placed in a house in Hawaii with two goals: find their perfect match, and win a million dollars. The couples start pairing off, fights break out, and heartbreak

episodes.name: The Temptation of Chris T
episodes.overview: Chris T & Shanley take their relationship to the next level, Simone & John are on separate pages, the cast competes in their second challenge, and a love triangle forms.

episodes.name: A Real "G"
episodes.overview: Chris S. continues to play mind games with Paige, Ethan reveals his insecurities to Amber, Brittany pursues Adam, and tensions rise when Simone confronts Jacy.

episodes.name: Karma’s a Bitch
episodes.overview: The boys experience a blast from the past at the getaway challenge, Coleysia stakes her claims on Dillan, and Adam drops a truth bomb on Brittany.

episodes.name: Double Shot
episodes.overview: Tension reaches a boiling point between John and Simone; Kayla is interested in Wes and Ryan; a waterfall challenge sends two couples to the Truth Booth.

episodes.name: Turn the Paige
episodes.overview: Shanley loses her cool when Simone tries to separate her from Chris T., Paige feels the sting of rejection, and Kayla finally has to deal with the love triangle she created.

episodes.name: It's So Hard... to Say Goodbye
episodes.overview: Shanley has a face off with Simone over the Truth Booth drama, Kayla's jealous side comes out, and Paige has ups and downs with Chris S.

episodes.name: Getting Dumped On
episodes.overview: The cast is finally fed up with Kayla and confronts her about her manipulation and lies, Ryan reevaluates his feelings for her, and Chris S. tries to get in between Jacy and John J

episodes.name: White Party
episodes.overview: The cast lets loose at a White Party, Shanley gets serious about her feelings for Chris T., and the love triangle between Jacy, John, and Chris S. finally blows up.

episodes.name: Rub Down With a Happy Ending
episodes.overview: The cast compete in a sexy rubdown challenge, Jacy is still confused about John and Scali, and the fate of the house could be affected by one cast member's Truth Booth decision.

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: All of the season secrets, drama, and unsettled business comes out during the reunion episode while different cast members take turns in the hot seat.

episodes.name: One Too Many
episodes.overview: The wild adventure begins with all new singles looking for love and money. The cast gets to know one another, hook-ups happen, relationships form, and an 11th girl is brought on to shake things up.

episodes.name: The Truth Will Cost You
episodes.overview: Relationships continue to form and several couples become convinced they've found their match. Brandon and Christina stick together, while something personal allows Briana to become closer to Curtis. Layton is confused over Jess and Jenni.

episodes.name: Virgin Tears
episodes.overview: The house can't agree on a strategy, Nate loses his cool over Shelby, Christina tries to move on with little help from Brandon, and Jenni sees a side to Layton that isn't pleasant.

episodes.name: Loose Lips Sink Relationships
episodes.overview: An alcohol-fueled mistake threatens the strongest couple in the house; Anthony goes after Layton's crush; John makes a move on Christina; the house reels after a Matchup Ceremony.

episodes.name: Strap Those Boots Tight
episodes.overview: The house is stunned by the last Matchup Ceremony; Jenni thinks that Layton is her match, but worries about Jessica; the Truth Booth threatens another couple.

episodes.name: Parental Guidance
episodes.overview: The ladies' parents arrive to interrogate the guys; tension boils over between Layton and Anthony; the house learns that history can repeat itself.

episodes.name: Hot Salsa
episodes.overview: After a failed Matchup Ceremony, the house is eager for a fresh start; John believes he found his match in Jenni; Ashley ends up in a love triangle.

episodes.name: Dumped
episodes.overview: Dario and Layton's battle over Ashley intensifies; Ellie is interested in Nathan, but Nathan thinks Christina is his perfect match; Christina can not handle the pressure.

episodes.name: Old Flames
episodes.overview: Nathan is not happy after Christina gets back together with Brandon. Ashley's indecision over Layton and Dario could cost the house the win.

episodes.name: One Switch, One Glitch
episodes.overview: The house has a final match-up ceremony, with the last switch.

episodes.name: Once in a Lifetime Chance Brings Romance
Libido Limbo
episodes.overview: Confirmed non-matches continue hooking up despite the presence of possible new love interests; Kiki moves in on Chuck, which upsets Hannah; and the house is called out for not moving on.

episodes.name: Breaking Point
episodes.overview: Amanda pops off, again, but this time the fallout is much bigger than the house could have anticipated. The house strategizes to throw the challenge in order to send the right couple into the Truth Booth.

episodes.name: Never Give Up On Love
episodes.overview: Couples are torn between playing for love and strategizing to win. The house decides to let a coin toss decide their fate. Can they turn 25 cents into $750,000?

episodes.name: Perfect Match at First Sight
episodes.overview: This episode doesn't have a summary yet. Add one here.

episodes.name: Punch Drunk Love
episodes.overview: When John's relationship with Julia takes a turn, he loses it; Asaf and Francesca's status is in question; Keylen shocks the house with a revelation about her relationship with Gio.

episodes.name: She Don't Want You
episodes.overview: John goes off when Stephen makes a play for Julia. Tori and Camille set their sights on the same guy. The pressure is on for the “golden couples” heading into the Truth Booth.

episodes.name: Three's a Crowd
episodes.overview: Gio and Kaylen's perfect relationship starts to fall apart, throwing the house into turmoil; Asaf sleeps with the wrong person.

episodes.name: Mammas' Boys
episodes.overview: The guys' mothers reveal embarrassing information; Stephen becomes increasingly paranoid; Francesca is caught in Gio's wolf den.

episodes.name: All or Nothing
episodes.overview: An epic fight leads to astonishment and tears; the group believes in one set of matches; Asaf wants to follow his heart.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: This episode doesn't have a summary yet. Add one here.

episodes.name: Playing The Game and Getting Played
episodes.overview: Andre does a 180 when his relationship with Alicia hits the rocks. Gianna is torn between the nice guy and the bad boy. The house tries to follow their hearts but their hearts are all over the place

episodes.name: Butthurt
episodes.overview: Love quadrangles erupt and cause chaos in the house.  Exes swap partners for some romantic alone time on the getaway date from hell.  Tyler breaks Taylor’s heart by making moves on multiple girls.

episodes.name: Tyranny of Love
episodes.overview: Tyranny convinces the house that she has found her match.  Tyler’s behavior opens the door for Andre to make his move on Taylor.  Gianna and Hayden take their non-match relationship to the next level.

episodes.name: Sex, Lies, and Truth Booths
episodes.overview: Alicia betrays her friendship with Kam. A lie detector test puts Tyler on the spot in front of the entire house. Gianna strings Hayden along while sparks reignite with Michael.

episodes.name: No Bro-Code
episodes.overview: Distraught over learning about another non-match, Alicia moves in on someone else’s man.  Tyler’s confession makes Shannon question his intentions.  The guys best friends break bro-code and reveal some embarrassing secrets.

episodes.name: Party Hard, Love Harder
episodes.overview: Tensions between love triangles erupt at a Dominican Carnival blow out. Hayden and Carolina make moves towards a deeper relationship. The house grapples with how to deal with non-match couples.

episodes.name: Relationship Rehab
episodes.overview: Tensions erupt in the house when non-match couples stand their ground and refuse to separate. Things get serious between Hayden and Carolina, leaving Gianna heartbroken. The girls' exes don't live up to expectations.

episodes.name: Between a Rock and a Love Place
episodes.overview: An altercation during a house party threatens Michael's relationship with Kathryn. Strategy tries to tear couples apart and forces Shannon to choose between listening to the house or following her heart.

episodes.name: Eleven Is the Magic Number
episodes.overview: A desperate house has one more chance to win love and money. Kathryn and Ozzy reconnect. The house tries to open Hannah's eyes to the reality of her relationship.

episodes.name: Swipe Right for Love
episodes.overview: 22 singles move into a house in New Orleans to try and pair up as 11 perfect matches and win, $1,000,000.  As couples fall for each other hard and fast, love triangles form.

episodes.name: Shot Through the Heart
episodes.overview: Malcom finds himself caught between Diandra and Nurys; Keith and Alexis try to break each other's hearts.

episodes.name: Love in Limbo
episodes.overview: The strongest couples' connections are questioned; Michael tries to break up multiple relationships.

episodes.name: Bae-trayl
episodes.overview: Frustration grows between couples that are in too deep and singles who are struggling to make connections.

episodes.name: Jelly AF
episodes.overview: Chaos erupts in the house when Kareem’s attraction to Zoe pushes Alivia to tears. The girls decide to go with strategy during the Match-Up Ceremony, leaving everyone nervous.

episodes.name: Don't come at me crazy
episodes.overview: Jada rages when Uche calls her out for making moves on Clinton. Two on-again-off-gain couples are back on. The girls’ families share some embarrassing info.

episodes.name: Sinking Relation-ships
episodes.overview: Nurys can’t handle Malcolm and Diandra becoming a thing. The house is divided between ride-or-die couples who refuse to separate and singles who have a hard time making connections.

episodes.name: Ex-tra Cray
episodes.overview: Kareem and Alexis are pushed over the edge when Alivia and Keith explore the possibility that they’re a Perfect Match. Exes arrive to spill some tea, including one ex that everyone already knows.

episodes.name: Tale of Two Players
episodes.overview: Paranoia sets in when Audrey sees Michael making a connection with Geles.  Malcolm faces the music for his player ways and the house starts to explore new connections.

episodes.name: Reunion: The Final Matchup (Part 1)
episodes.overview: After weeks of searching for love and playing for money, the Season 6 cast reunites to give insider info on the explosive moments, spill tea on the unseen drama, and reveal what's gone down since leaving the house.

6.name: Season 6
6.overview: Set in the stunning city of New Orleans, Season 6 is tasking a crew of love hopefuls with two things: To dig deeper than ever before to find true love and to keep from screwing it all up. Though chances are, having the Big Easy as your backdrop doesn't make either of those to-do items any, er, easier.

episodes.name: Leap of Fate
episodes.overview: 22 singles move into a house in Hawaii to try and pair up as 11 perfect matches and win, $1,000,000. Jealousy takes over when couples form quickly. Zak provokes the wrath of Bria and Tevin and Kenya's player ways threaten their budding romance.

episodes.name: Flirt at Your Own Risk
episodes.overview: Zak provokes the wrath of Bria and Tevin and Kenya’s player ways threaten their budding romance.

episodes.name: With Frenemies Like These...
episodes.overview: Zak explores his options while the women fight each other for his attention. Kenya and Jasmine officially become enemies.

episodes.name: A Boyfriend by Any Other Name
episodes.overview: Asia is hurt when she learns what her friend and her crush did behind her back. Cali and Brett's budding romance is jeopardized by their own bad dating habits.

episodes.name: Ex-tracurricular Activities
episodes.overview: The house is shook when their exes show up to spend some quality time. Tension soars when one ex threatens to break up a power couple and another gets aggressive. Zak is torn between Bria and Morgan.

episodes.name: Spilling the Tea
episodes.overview: Kwasi starts drama when he lets slip what Tevin and Jasmine did the night before; Bria is angered by Morgan and Zak's developing relationship; the house makes some risky choices in picking their matches.

episodes.name: He Loves Me Not
episodes.overview: Cam starts to question his relationship with Kayla; Daniel's fun and games push Sam away; the house faces its most important Truth Booth yet.

episodes.name: Beast Mode
episodes.overview: Tensions erupt between Cam and Kwasi when Kwasi makes moves on Kayla; Asia explodes when she thinks certain people in the house are being shady; Zak has a choice to make.

episodes.name: I Want You To Want Me
episodes.overview: Nutsa crushes on Brett while Brett's inability to get over Cali has consequences for the entire house. Moe is pushed to start playing the game. Lewis reveals his true feelings to Asia.

episodes.name: Master Plan
episodes.overview: Bria’s obsession with Zak and Zak’s player ways threaten the house’s ability to play the game. Cali comes up with a plan to find out which of the power couples are a Perfect Match and which are not.

episodes.name: Once Upon a Crazy Party Time
episodes.overview: At a wild party, questionable behavior turns best friends into best enemies; Tevin and Kenya get ready to learn their fate; Moe is pushed to step up his game.

episodes.name: Caught on Kiss Cam
episodes.overview: Kwasi and Jasmine's connection is put in jeopardy when a familiar foe makes a move on their relationship; power couples try to make new connections.

episodes.name: This Is Nuts-a
episodes.overview: Brett is put on the hot seat when he second guesses his feelings for Nutsa. The house is in crisis mode as they scramble to figure out the perfect matches.

episodes.name: It All Comes Down to This
episodes.overview: Asia attempts to sabotage Sam's relationship with Daniel; the house gets one final chance to win love and money and an extra day to deal with the fallout.

episodes.name: Reunion the Final Matchup
episodes.overview: After weeks of searching for love and playing for money, the Season 7 cast reunites to give insider info on the explosive moments, spill tea on the unseen drama, and reveal what’s gone down since leaving the house.

episodes.name: Come One, Come All (1)
episodes.overview: For the first time, love has no limits and everyone is an option as 16 singles arrive in Hawaii to find love and win $1,000,000.

episodes.name: Come One, Come All (2)
episodes.overview: There is already trouble in paradise for the strongest couples; one couple struggles with the concept of open relationships; love triangles are reconfigured.

episodes.name: This Is Trash
episodes.overview: Justin is caught between someone who wants him and someone who is unsure about the future; Basit struggles for acceptance; the house faces some uncomfortable "truths."

episodes.name: We Come to Slay
episodes.overview: After queer prom, the house is a literal and figurative mess; dramatic make outs spell doom for two couples; Dionne Slay arrives.

episodes.name: There Was A Fivesome?
episodes.overview: A fivesome shakes up the dynamics of the house. Justin’s self-destructive tendencies threaten his relationship with Max. Danny makes a connection.

episodes.name: Hate To Burst Your Bubble
episodes.overview: The house is determined to figure out which of the power couples is a Perfect Match. Jonathan is determined to burst a love bubble. Kai moves on in front of Jenna’s face.

episodes.name: Red Flag Alert
episodes.overview: Jonathan tries to make amends with Basit. One couple grows closer while others struggle to overcome toxic dating behaviors.

episodes.name: This Sucks and Blows
episodes.overview: Friends and family put the house on blast; Jenna tries to navigate strategy versus heart; a trip to the "Boom Boom Room" has explosive consequences.

episodes.name: Games Players Play
episodes.overview: Tensions flare during the house party, Paige begins to drop her guard, and the singles try to convince Kai that his flirtatious behavior is hurting others.

episodes.name: It All Comes Down to Jax
episodes.overview: Three couples find out that they are a Perfect Match and two couples get bad news. Justin and Max get answers. Paige struggles to let down her walls.

episodes.name: On to the Next
episodes.overview: With five strategically confirmed perfect matches and devastating news for one pair, the singles compete in a challenge to see which of the "stragglers" are perfectly aligned.

episodes.name: All or Nothing
episodes.overview: With six singles left and $750,000 on the line, the housemates must discover each other's love languages and figure out the final three couples before their last matchup ceremony.

episodes.name: How Far Would You Go For Love? (1)
episodes.overview: Love connections instantly spark when 22 unlucky in love singles from around the world move into a house in the Canary Islands to see if they can find their perfect match and win $1 million.

episodes.name: How Far Would You Go For Love? (2)
episodes.overview: A night one couple separates and moves on to new connections while other couples think they have found 'the one.' Pressure boils when romantic connections are put to the test at the first Match Up Ceremony.

episodes.name: Rollercoaster Relationships
episodes.overview: After a heartbreaking match up ceremony, some singles struggle to explore new connections while others make selfish decisions that affect the rest of the house. Honest conversations about wants and needs lead to hurt feelings.

episodes.name: Love Is Heaven, Finding It Is Hell
episodes.overview: A house party sparks new romantic connections, and a love triangle begins to form when one single second guesses their night one connection.

episodes.name: Wants and Needs
episodes.overview: A truth booth reveal shakes up the house, leaving one couple in an awkward love triangle. Another couple is forced to end their relationship after pressure from the house begins to weigh in on them.

episodes.name: Down The Rabbit Hole
episodes.overview: When the singles let loose at a party, jealousy threatens to keep one couple from going on their getaway date. Frustration arises when the house realizes that only one of their strongest couples can be a perfect match.

episodes.name: It Takes One To Know One
episodes.overview: Surprise visitors give the singles advice and insights into what it takes to find their perfect match. A Truth Booth reveal changes the dynamics in the house.

episodes.name: Striking Out
episodes.overview: In an unprecedented moment, Kamie reveals a perfect match at the match up ceremony. A favorite couple finally learns their fate. Another couple undoes their breakup.

episodes.name: Kiss and Tell
episodes.overview: Will faces the consequences of trying to keep his relationship with Courtney while looking for his perfect match. The house lets loose and shares hidden talents.

episodes.name: You Were The One
episodes.overview: After weeks of debating with each other about how to find their matches, the singles band together and make their riskiest effort yet at finding true love.
